#: includes/classes/class-settings.php:557
msgid "Automatically convert keywords to shortlinks in post content."
msgstr "Samodejno pretvori ključne besede v kratke povezave v vsebini objave."

#: includes/classes/class-settings.php:558
msgid ""
"When enabled, keywords configured in shortlink settings will be "
"automatically linked in your content."
msgstr ""
"Ko je omogočeno, bodo ključne besede, konfigurirane v nastavitvah kratkih "
"povezav, samodejno povezane v vaši vsebini."

#: includes/classes/class-settings.php:564
msgid "Open Auto-Links In"
msgstr "Odpri samodejne povezave v"

#: includes/classes/class-settings.php:565
msgid "Choose how auto-linked keywords should open."
msgstr "Izberite, kako naj se odpirajo samodejno povezane ključne besede."

#: includes/classes/class-settings.php:567
msgid "Same tab"
msgstr "Enaka zavihek"

#: includes/classes/class-settings.php:568
msgid "New tab"
msgstr "Nov zavihek"

#: includes/classes/class-settings.php:576
msgid "Auto-Link Color"
msgstr "Barva samodejne povezave"

#: includes/classes/class-settings.php:577
msgid "Choose the color for auto-linked keywords."
msgstr "Izberite barvo za samodejno povezana ključna beseda."

#: includes/classes/class-settings.php:588
msgid "Auto-List Links"
msgstr "Samodejno seznam povezav"

#: includes/classes/class-settings.php:593
msgid "Auto-List Shortlinks"
msgstr "Samodejno seznam povezav"

#: includes/classes/class-settings.php:594
msgid ""
"When enabled, shortlinks will appear in the \"All Links\" table based on "
"the behavior you configure below."
msgstr ""
"Ko je omogočeno, se bodo kratke povezave pojavile v tabeli \"Vse povezave\" "
"glede na obnašanje, ki ga konfigurirate spodaj."

#: includes/classes/class-settings.php:600
msgid "Configure Post Types"
msgstr "Konfiguriraj vrste objav"

#: includes/classes/class-settings.php:601
msgid "Set when links should be auto-listed for each post type"
msgstr "Nastavite, kdaj naj se povezave samodejno seznamijo za vsako vrsto objave"

#: includes/classes/class-settings.php:602
msgid ""
"Add post types and configure when their shortlinks should appear in the "
"\"All Links\" table. Changes are saved automatically."
msgstr ""
"Dodajte vrste objav in konfigurirajte, kdaj naj se njihove kratke povezave "
"pojavijo v tabeli \"Vse povezave\". Spremembe se shranijo samodejno."

#: includes/classes/class-settings.php:609
#: includes/classes/class-statuses.php:233
msgid "Post Status Visibility"
msgstr "Vidnost statusa objave"

#: includes/classes/class-settings.php:614
msgid "Allowed Post Statuses"
msgstr "Dovoljeni statusi objav"

#: includes/classes/class-settings.php:623
msgid "Unpublished Content Notice"
msgstr "Obvestilo o neobjavljenem vsebini"

#: includes/classes/class-settings.php:624
msgid ""
"Show a frontend notice when an internal shortlink displays a post that is "
"not published."
msgstr ""
"Prikažite obvestilo na sprednjem delu, ko notranja kratka povezava prikaže "
"objavo, ki ni objavljena."

#: includes/classes/class-settings.php:630
msgid "Notice Post Statuses"
msgstr "Obvestilo o statusih objav"

#: includes/classes/class-settings.php:631
msgid ""
"This notice only applies to internal shortlinks that render post content "
"directly. External shortlinks are not affected."
msgstr ""
"To obvestilo se uporablja samo za notranje kratke povezave, ki neposredno "
"prikazujejo vsebino objave. Zunanje kratke povezave niso prizadete."

#: includes/classes/class-settings.php:640
msgid "Notice Messages"
msgstr "Obvestila sporočil"

#: includes/classes/class-settings.php:654
msgid "Default redirection method for shortlinks"
msgstr "Privzeta metoda preusmeritve za kratke povezave"

#: includes/classes/class-settings.php:666
msgid "Mark links as sponsored content"
msgstr "Označite povezave kot sponzorirano vsebino"

#: includes/classes/class-settings.php:674
msgid "Prevent search engines from following links"
msgstr "Preprečite iskalnikom, da sledijo povezavam"

#: includes/classes/class-settings.php:682
msgid "Pass URL parameters to target links"
msgstr "Prenesite URL parametre na ciljne povezave"

#: includes/classes/class-settings.php:695
msgid "Secure your shortlinks"
msgstr "Zavarujte svoje kratke povezave"

#: includes/classes/class-settings.php:696
msgid "Users must enter a password to redirect to the target link."
msgstr "Uporabniki morajo vnesti geslo, da se preusmerijo na ciljno povezavo."

#: includes/classes/class-settings.php:702
msgid "Default Password"
msgstr "Privzeto geslo"

#: includes/classes/class-settings.php:703
msgid "Default password for protected links"
msgstr "Privzeto geslo za zaščitene povezave"

#: includes/classes/class-settings.php:704
msgid ""
"This password will be used for links that have password protection enabled "
"via global settings. Passwords are case sensitive."
msgstr ""
"To geslo bo uporabljeno za povezave, ki imajo zaščito z geslom omogočeno "
"preko globalnih nastavitev. Gesla so občutljiva na velike in male črke."

#: includes/classes/class-settings.php:715
msgid "Set an expiration date and time for shortlinks"
msgstr "Nastavite datum in čas poteka za kratke povezave"

#: includes/classes/class-settings.php:723
msgid "Select the date when this shortlink should stop working"
msgstr "Izberite datum, ko naj ta kratka povezava preneha delovati"

#: includes/classes/class-settings.php:736
msgid "Select the time when the shortlink should expire"
msgstr "Izberite čas, ko naj kratka povezava poteče"

#: includes/classes/class-settings.php:755
msgid "Revisions"
msgstr "Revizije"

#: includes/classes/class-settings.php:760
msgid "Revision Link Visibility"
msgstr "Vidnost povezav revizij"

#: includes/classes/class-settings.php:761
msgid ""
"When enabled, revision shortlinks will appear in the \"All Shortlinks\" "
"table based on the behavior you configure below."
msgstr ""
"Ko je omogočeno, se bodo kratke povezave revizij pojavile v tabeli \"Vse "
"kratke povezave\" glede na obnašanje, ki ga konfigurirate spodaj."

#: includes/classes/class-settings.php:763
msgid "When Revision is Created"
msgstr "Ko je revizija ustvarjena"

#: includes/classes/class-settings.php:765
msgid "When Revision is Created or Link is First Used"
msgstr "Ko je revizija ustvarjena ali je povezava prvič uporabljena"

#: includes/classes/class-settings.php:773
msgid "Show Shortlink in Revision Table"
msgstr "Prikaži kratko povezavo v tabeli revizij"

#: includes/classes/class-settings.php:774
msgid "Display shortlink column when viewing revisions in PublishPress Revisions."
msgstr ""
"Prikaži stolpec kratkih povezav pri ogledovanju revizij v PublishPress "
"Revizijah."

#: includes/classes/class-settings.php:780
msgid "Revision Visibility for Visitors"
msgstr "Vidnost revizij za obiskovalce"

#: includes/classes/class-settings.php:781
msgid "Allow logged-out visitors to view revision content via shortlinks."
msgstr ""
"Dovoli odjavljenim obiskovalcem, da si ogledajo vsebino revizij prek "
"kratkih povezav."

#: includes/classes/class-settings.php:782
msgid ""
"By default, PublishPress Revisions blocks visitors from viewing revision "
"previews. When enabled, revision shortlinks will render the revision "
"content directly for logged-out visitors instead of redirecting to the "
"preview URL."
msgstr ""
"Privzeto PublishPress Revizije blokira obiskovalce pri ogledu predogledov "
"revizij. Ko je omogočeno, bodo kratke povezave revizij prikazale vsebino "
"revizij neposredno za odjavljenimi obiskovalci namesto, da bi preusmerile "
"na URL predogleda."

